My personal go-to holiday makeup look using @bobbibrown Luxe eye and cheek palette. @bobbibrown luxe shadows are a favorite of mine, I have just about every shade in my kit. The shimmer is silky and soft while picking up just the right amount of light. Love love 💕 

Beauty breakdown @bobbibrown 
Vitamin Enriched face base 
Skin long wear weightless foundation warm ivory
Skin full cover concealer beige
Highlighting powder sunset glow (I double this as my blush) 
Long wear cream shadow stick mulberry 
Luxe eye and cheek palette, shades in order of application:  Hazel, sunset, overheated Copper Glow highlighting powder 
Luxe defining lipstick avant gardenia 

 #BBpartner

A simple way to achieve a natural, lightweight and fully contoured base using corrector and concealer. This is something I do on my clients as well as on myself when looking to create definition. I prefer to use creamy products that blend into the skin really well so it looks seamless and makes it easy to work with.
 
Beauty Breakdown @bobbibrown
Skin Long-wear Weightless Foundation in shade 3.5
Skin Corrector Stick in shade peach
Skin Full Cover Concealer in shade sand 
Pot Rouge for Lips and Cheeks in shade fresh melon
Luxe Lipstick in shade neutral rose 
 
#bobbibrown #Fullcoveragemyway #BBpartner AD

Bigger brighter eyes that are mess-free and transfer-proof, especially for those crease-less eyes like mine!  A staple in my kit, the @bobbibrown long-wear cream shadow sticks allow for extra-defined shadow application, like when creating a wing or defining a crease, to help you to create clean lines and fine points. You just can’t get the same result, or staying power, with a traditional powder.  @bobbibrown Longwear cream shadow sticks in bone, cinnamon and truffle. Perfectly defined gel eyeliner black  #BobbiBrownPartner #BobbiBrownCosmetics #AD

All day wear summer base with @lancome.official power duo Teint Idole Ultra Wear Foundation and Teint Idole Ultra Wear All Over Concealer. 

Not only does this feel completely weightless and undetectable up close, it created a base that locked in the rest of the makeup I applied after! I’ve never had my blush and contour stay on so well! And no shiny t-zone. A real summer staple! #teintidoleultrawear #unrealultrawear #lancomepartner
